Original: Ahh, another request from Dalla at the
Saehrimnir Inn. I believe you all know
her quite well by now.
[Page]
She wants you to... oomph, fill this
barrel with the [Color:5]apples[Color:0] that can be
found in the [Color:5]Sacred Mountains[Color:0].
[Page]
Given the barrel's size... I think
around [Color:5]4[Color:0] would fit. You'll want to be
selective with what you pick.
[Page]
I did not know apples grew in that
frigid land, but I am excited to see
what Dalla has in store for them.
[Page]
Well, take care, and I shall await
your swift return.

explorers' strength and cunning to
